rbnXAal5VclStatMIB.name: rbnXAal5VclStatMIB
rbnXAal5VclStatMIB.contactinfo: RedBack Networks, Inc. Postal: 1389 Moffett Park Drive Sunnyvale, CA 94089-1134 USA Phone: +1 408 548 3500 Fax: +1 408 548 3599 E-mail: mib-info@RedBackNetworks.com
rbnXAal5VclStatMIB.description: The MIB for instrumenting statistics associated with an ATM VCL. This MIB is positioned in the RedBack Networks experimental MIB space because it mirrors MIB objects currently being developed by the IETF atommib Working Group, namely the atmAal5VclStatTable objects found in the ATM2-MIB (draft-ietf-atommib-atm2-XX.txt). At such time as the ATM2-MIB is placed on the IETF standards track, this MIB will be obsoleted in favor of the IETF one

rbnXAtmAal5VclStatTable.name: rbnXAtmAal5VclStatTable
rbnXAtmAal5VclStatTable.description: This table provides a collection of objects providing AAL5 configuration and performance statistics of a VCL.

rbnXAtmAal5VclStatEntry.name: rbnXAtmAal5VclStatEntry
rbnXAtmAal5VclStatEntry.description: Each entry in this table represents a VCL.

rbnXAtmAal5VclInPkts.name: rbnXAtmAal5VclInPkts
rbnXAtmAal5VclInPkts.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs received on the AAL5 VCC at the interface identified by the ifIndex.

rbnXAtmAal5VclOutPkts.name: rbnXAtmAal5VclOutPkts
rbnXAtmAal5VclOutPkts.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs transmitted on the AAL5 VCC at the interface identified by the ifIndex.

rbnXAtmAal5VclInOctets.name: rbnXAtmAal5VclInOctets
rbnXAtmAal5VclInOctets.description: The number of octets contained in AAL5 CPCS PDUs received on the AAL5 VCC at the interface identified by the ifIndex.

rbnXAtmAal5VclOutOctets.name: rbnXAtmAal5VclOutOctets
rbnXAtmAal5VclOutOctets.description: The number of octets contained in AAL5 CPCS PDUs transmitted on the AAL5 VCC at the interface identified by the ifIndex.

rbnXAal5VclStatMIBCompliance.name: rbnXAal5VclStatMIBCompliance
rbnXAal5VclStatMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for RedBack Networks SNMP entities which represent AAL5 VCL statistics

rbnXAal5VclStatGroup.name: rbnXAal5VclStatGroup
rbnXAal5VclStatGroup.description: A collection of objects providing supplemental AAL5 VCL information beyond that supplied by IETF standards-track MIBs
